Parameter ID:         pend (0x0020)
Description:          Indicates which DTMF digits map to a prompt end key operation. On detection
Type:                 String
Optional:             Yes
Possible values:      A sequence of one or more characters from the set 0-9, A-D or a-d, *, and #
Default:              None.
